\
And the word of the\'a0Lord\'a0came to him: \'93What are you doing here, Elijah?\'94\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl0
\fs24 \cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}This is the question we need to all ask today.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl0
\f1\b \cf5 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}What are you doing here?\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl1
\f2\b0 \cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}At River Lake\
\pard\tx1660\tx2160\pardeftab720\li2160\fi-2160\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl2\cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Attending vs Engaging\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Gifted vs Giving\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl0\cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Let me back up a little though and ask a broader question: What are you doing HERE?\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Whatever and where ever you\'92re running to\'85what are you doing?\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Elijah is Hiding from something\'85He is hiding from someone actually.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Fear has him in his hiding place\
\pard\pardeftab720\li360\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls9\ilvl0
\f1\b \cf5 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Are you running toward something right now or away from something?\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls9\ilvl1
\f2\b0 \cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Too often people make decisions and they lie to themselves like Elijah is lying to himself. \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}He told himself in his fake humility he was just no better than others and so let God kill him.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}But the reality was that he was running the call God had put on his life because he deemed it too hard and scary so he fled.  \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls9\ilvl0\cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The danger is the running can look the same for both!\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls9\ilvl1\cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You can quit the same job for two completely different reasons\
\pard\tx1660\tx2160\pardeftab720\li2160\fi-2160\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls9\ilvl2\cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I hate this job and I don\'92t know what I\'92m going to do next but I\'92m done here\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I believe God is calling me to take a huge leap of faith and while it is scary and I\'92m not clear about what to do next I\'92m confident in the direction I\'92m going.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Same decision but for two different reasons and only you know the real reason you\'92re doing what you\'92re doing.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls9\ilvl0
\f1\b \cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}So, what are you doing here?\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f3\fs20 \cf7 \super 10\'a0
\f2\b0\fs28 \nosupersub He replied, \'93I have been very zealous\'a0for the\'a0Lord\'a0God Almighty. The Israelites have rejected your covenant,\'a0torn down your altars,\'a0and put your prophets to death with the sword. I am the only one left,\'a0and now they are trying to kill me too.\'94\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls10\ilvl0
\fs24 \cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And it is here we see the full power of FEAR in the Clickbait in our heads\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It is a lie that drives away from our calling and deceives us on so many levels\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Elijah has\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls10\ilvl1\cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Run from God\'92s will\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Run from all friends / family\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Stuck in mountains over hundred miles from his calling.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls10\ilvl0\cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Why?  Because of \'91Those people\'92\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls10\ilvl1\cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}IT\'92S BLAME!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}If you look at what he says he comes off perfect and awesome and EVERYONE else is terrible.  He\'92s the ONLY ONE who really loves God and if THOSE PEOPLE would just get in line it would be ok.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls10\ilvl0\cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Again, the Clickbait of fear can make us feel things that aren\'92t true.\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls10\ilvl1\cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}He isn\'92t alone\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It isn\'92t that bad\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And it really is no different than before but he\'92s scared.  And fear does something to us when we allow it into our minds\'85when we go there and allow the narrative to speak about our future.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f3\b\fs20 \cf7 \super 11\'a0
\f2\b0\fs28 \nosupersub The\'a0Lord\'a0said, \'93Go out and stand on the mountain\'a0in the presence of the\'a0Lord, for the\'a0Lord\'a0is about to pass by.\'94\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf7 \
