\f1\b\fs24 \cf9 Transition:  So God does this incredible show of power to remind him of who He is.\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls11\ilvl0
\f2\b0 \cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}To demonstrate His power over others\'92 power.\
